OL,3,COptimism surges among UK firms but
OL,4,Cuncertainties remain ` HSBC
OL,6,FUK firms are at a "positive inflection
OL,7,Fpoint" with a new government in place
OL,8,Fand amid a tech-fuelled boom but
OL,9,Funcertainties loom large ahead of the
OL,10,FUS election and as Middle Eastern
OL,11,Ftensions escalate, according to HSBC's
OL,12,Fcommercial banking boss.
OL,14,FStuart Tait, head of commercial
OL,15,Fbanking at HSBC UK, said the banking
OL,16,Fgiant's latest annual capital
OL,17,Fexpenditure (Capex) report reveals
OL,18,Fthat "optimism is climbing and
OL,19,Fambitions are rising to match".
