OL,3,COptimism surges among UK firms but
OL,4,Cuncertainties remain ` HSBC
OL,6,FMore than half of UK businesses (55%)
OL,7,Fare positive about growth in the year
OL,8,Fahead, up 9% on last year, according
OL,9,Fto the study.
OL,11,FThe report, which is compiled from a
OL,12,Fsurvey of 1,583 HSBC business
OL,13,Fcustomers, showed that two thirds of
OL,14,Ffirms have growth ambitions, up from
OL,15,F64% last year, with more than a fifth
OL,16,F(22%) looking to grow by at least 20%
OL,17,F` the highest recorded since the
OL,18,Freport was launched four years ago.
