OL,3,COptimism surges among UK firms but
OL,4,Cuncertainties remain ` HSBC
OL,6,FMr Tait said the poll ` conducted at
OL,7,Fthe end of July, following the UK
OL,8,Felection ` showed a "bounce in
OL,9,Foptimism" and "offers many signs of a
OL,10,Fpositive inflection point".
OL,12,FHe told the PA news agency: "Firms
OL,13,Fwere just waiting for the election to
OL,14,Fbe done.
OL,16,F"The UK had a very smooth and
OL,17,Fstraightforward election and we saw a
OL,18,Fflurry of activity afterwards, with
OL,19,Fmergers and acquisitions and capex
OL,20,Fspend.
