OL,3,COptimism surges among UK firms but
OL,4,Cuncertainties remain ` HSBC
OL,6,F"They were just waiting for that
OL,7,Fmilestone to pass."
OL,9,FBut Mr Tait said attentions have now
OL,10,Fturned to the upcoming Budget from new
OL,11,FChancellor Rachel Reeves, as well as
OL,12,Fthe impending US election and the
OL,13,Fprospect of further interest rate cuts
OL,14,Fin the UK.
OL,16,FThe current tensions in the Middle
OL,17,FEast are casting another cloud of
OL,18,Funcertainty for businesses, with
OL,19,Fworries over what may happen to oil
OL,20,Fprices, which have already risen
OL,21,Fsharply in recent days.
