OL,3,COptimism surges among UK firms but
OL,4,Cuncertainties remain ` HSBC
OL,6,F"Everybody is watching that very
OL,7,Fclosely," said Mr Tait, pointing out
OL,8,Fthat the recent strikes in US ports
OL,9,Fare also a possible concern among
OL,10,Fbusinesses.
OL,12,F"What matters to many businesses is
OL,13,Fthe free flow of trade," he said.
OL,15,FBut Mr Tait said UK firms have become
OL,16,Fadept at navigating challenging
OL,17,Fsituations, having endured Covid, the
OL,18,Fsupply chain crisis that followed and
OL,19,Fthe energy price shock after Russia
OL,20,Finvaded Ukraine.
