OL,3,COptimism surges among UK firms but
OL,4,Cuncertainties remain ` HSBC
OL,6,F"Some of the shocks that have come
OL,7,Falong in the past three to five years
OL,8,Fhave proved that UK businesses are
OL,9,Fmore resilient and able to navigate...
OL,10,Fbetter than we would've previously
OL,11,Fexpected," he said.
OL,13,FThe report shows that technology is at
OL,14,Fthe heart of UK corporate growth
OL,15,Fambitions, with three quarters of
OL,16,Fthose looking to grow significantly
OL,17,Fplacing an importance on tech.
