OL,3,COptimism surges among UK firms but
OL,4,Cuncertainties remain ` HSBC
OL,6,FAnd tech firms are themselves among
OL,7,Fthe most cheery over prospects, thanks
OL,8,Flargely to the boom in artificial
OL,9,Fintelligence (AI), with 70% of IT
OL,10,Ffirms surveyed saying they are
OL,11,Foptimistic ` far outstripping
OL,12,Fcounterparts in other sectors.
OL,14,FIt also found that 81% of tech
OL,15,Fbusinesses are expecting to grow this
OL,16,Fyear, with more than a third (34%)
OL,17,Flooking for significant growth.
