OL,3,COptimism surges among UK firms but
OL,4,Cuncertainties remain ` HSBC
OL,6,FSectors that are more cautious over
OL,7,Fthe outlook are largely those with a
OL,8,Freliance on consumer spending ` which
OL,9,Fhas been under pressure in recent
OL,10,Fyears due to soaring costs ` such as
OL,11,Fhotels and restaurants as well as high
OL,12,Fstreet retailers.
OL,14,FHSBC found that 35% of hotels and
OL,15,Frestaurants are not optimistic,
OL,16,Ffollowed by more than a fifth (21%) of
OL,17,Fretail and wholesale firms.
