OL,3,COptimism surges among UK firms but
OL,4,Cuncertainties remain ` HSBC
OL,6,FWhile overall there is greater
OL,7,Foptimism among UK firms, the report
OL,8,Fshowed a fall in the number of
OL,9,Fcompanies planning to increase their
OL,10,Fspending over the next year ` at a
OL,11,Fthird, down from 38% last year.
OL,13,FHSBC said this may be down to the
OL,14,Fcontinuing burden of costs, though
OL,15,Fthese have eased recently, as well as
OL,16,Fthe perception that availability of
OL,17,Fcapital has narrowed.
OL,19,FBut it said despite this, where
OL,20,Finvestment is planned, more is being
OL,21,Fallocated to expansion and growth.
